    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到芬兰小屋8号，这是一座坐落在林间的经典夏日小屋，宁静得让你流连忘返！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297630/extras/f699cb5eaee393f85302ea863e758d60.poster.avif?t=1741990563\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297630/extras/f699cb5eaee393f85302ea863e758d60.webm?t=1741990563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297630/extras/f699cb5eaee393f85302ea863e758d60.mp4?t=1741990563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《芬兰小屋8号》是一款设定在mökki（夏日小屋）中的步行模拟游戏，mökki是芬兰夏日生活中不可或缺的一部分。游戏配备了必不可少的桑拿房和经典的芬兰天气预报广播节目，将带你穿越到千湖之国那宁静的夏日时光。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297630/extras/982f0f8fe46dd174e8f57cbc0f06b0dd.avif?t=1741990563\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297630/extras_big/982f0f8fe46dd174e8f57cbc0f06b0dd.avif?t=1741990563 width=800 height=640 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，在这座小屋中，某些不祥之物在你视线不及之处蠢蠢欲动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仔细观察，或许你能找到出路。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >坏消息是，你并非第一个尝试逃脱的人……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >好消息是，你并非第一个尝试逃脱的人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个秘密组织一直在调查这座小屋，他们的努力留下了一些便利的工具。这台笔记本电脑将帮助你识别你处于哪个循环中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297630/extras/0a68af7ddc6ba0e1c1484f312889e9fb.avif?t=1741990563\" width=614 height=348 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你发现异常，请从后门离开（标有“异常”胶带）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果未发现异常，则从前门离开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择正确，循环次数加1。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择错误，你将回到循环0。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一旦次数达到8，小屋或许会放你走……</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >平均游戏时长</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30至60分钟</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >语言支持</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏包含英语和芬兰语的音频，但游玩无需理解芬兰语。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏提供英语、乌克兰语、中文、俄语、芬兰语、西班牙语和日语版本。</p>",
